Currently, doing queries like the following is not allowed:
```
{
    Animal {
        out_Animal_ParentOf @optional {
            out_Animal_FedAt {
                name @output(out_name: "name")
            }
        }
    }
}
```

This is because we have no way to traverse out of an optional vertex in MATCH, so this issue is a blocker: https://github.com/orientechnologies/orientdb/issues/7803
